response.original_title: The Hunt For The Chicago Strangler
response.overview: A new docuseries is bringing national attention to the unsolved homicides of dozens of Chicago women. “The Hunt for the Chicago Strangler” is a three-part docuseries focused on the disappearances of at least 51 Chicago women who were all found strangled from 2001 to 2018.
response.title: The Hunt For The Chicago Strangler
